        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A bloodrager has powerful magical abilities that normally lie dormant. When a bloodrager taps into their power, either when they're angry or otherwise enter Rage, their magical power awakens and their blood becomes volatile and dangerous, harming their attackers and allowing them to cast a limited array of spells.</p><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>The Berserker</caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.UeNCm9oElbQEXre6]{Bloodrager Spellcasting}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.5F1s1v4KV38cuGGc]{Seething Blood}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.bo6PKpXxvPaRBBKo]{Savage Spellcasting} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.KQRBbG42MjUiR6im]{Wild Blood}, 3rd Level Bloodrager Spell</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>4th Level Bloodrager Spell</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>Seething Blood Improvement, 5th Level Bloodrager Spell</td></tr></tbody></table>",
